ED_Title: Comprehensive  implementation of and follow-up to the Vienna Declaration and Programme of Action
ED_DecisionText: At its 53rd plenary meeting, on 16 December 2021, the General Assembly took note of the report of the Third Committee. (Footnote: A/76/462/Add.4.)
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the main part of the session will be contained in document A/76/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
